      • getWeight

        double getWeight(StudentQuality.Context cx,
                 StudentQuality.Conflict c,
                 Enrollment e)
        Base weight of the given conflict and enrollment. Typically based on the StudentQuality.Conflict.getPenalty(), but change to be between 0.0 and 1.0. For example, for time conflicts, a percentage of share is used.
